getPropertyIDListFromSuggestion

Overview

This call is used to fetch suggestion list that matches the search term; it uses suggest service under BSGv3.

BSGv3 BSGv2 Show Additional Data Elements
Yes No

Additional Information

For further reading regarding BSG Elements:

  • Suggest Service

Request

Parameters

Parameter Description Required
op Operation Yes
uid User ID Yes
sid Session ID Yes
searchTerm Search Term Yes
includeUnits Include Units No
suggestionTypes Suggestion Types No
limit Limit List of Suggestions Yes
